#: ../../modules/digital/digital_gates.rst:2
msgid "Gates"
msgstr "Puertas"

#: ../../modules/digital/digital_gates.rst:4
msgid ""
"This submodule provides the necessary components to define and manipulate"
" quantum gates for use in digital quantum circuits."
msgstr ""
"Este submódulo proporciona los componentes necesarios para definir y "
"manipular puertas cuánticas para su uso en circuitos cuánticos digitales."

#: ../../modules/digital/digital_gates.rst:7
msgid "Simple Gates"
msgstr "Puertas simples"

#: ../../modules/digital/digital_gates.rst:9
msgid "Use these constructors to apply standard single- and two-qubit operations:"
msgstr "Use estos constructores para aplicar operaciones estándar de uno y dos qubits:"

#: ../../modules/digital/digital_gates.rst:11
msgid ""
":class:`X(qubit: int)<qilisdk.digital.gates.X>` Pauli X (bit-flip) on the"
" specified qubit."
msgstr ""
":class:`X(qubit: int)<qilisdk.digital.gates.X>` Pauli X (inversión de bit) "
"sobre el qubit especificado."

#: ../../modules/digital/digital_gates.rst:13
msgid ""
":class:`Y(qubit: int)<qilisdk.digital.gates.Y>` Pauli Y (bit-and-phase-"
"flip)."
msgstr ""
":class:`Y(qubit: int)<qilisdk.digital.gates.Y>` Pauli Y (inversión de bit "
"y fase)."

#: ../../modules/digital/digital_gates.rst:15
msgid ":class:`Z(qubit: int)<qilisdk.digital.gates.Z>` Pauli Z (phase-flip)."
msgstr ":class:`Z(qubit: int)<qilisdk.digital.gates.Z>` Pauli Z (inversión de fase)."

#: ../../modules/digital/digital_gates.rst:17
msgid ""
":class:`H(qubit: int)<qilisdk.digital.gates.H>` Hadamard: creates "
"superposition."
msgstr ""
":class:`H(qubit: int)<qilisdk.digital.gates.H>` Hadamard: crea "
"superposición."

#: ../../modules/digital/digital_gates.rst:19
msgid ""
":class:`I(qubit: int)<qilisdk.digital.gates.I>` Identity gate: leaves the"
" qubit unchanged."
msgstr ""
":class:`I(qubit: int)<qilisdk.digital.gates.I>` Puerta identidad: deja el "
"qubit sin cambios."

#: ../../modules/digital/digital_gates.rst:21
msgid ""
":class:`S(qubit: int)<qilisdk.digital.gates.S>` Phase gate (π/2 rotation "
"about Z)."
msgstr ""
":class:`S(qubit: int)<qilisdk.digital.gates.S>` Puerta de fase (rotación "
"π/2 alrededor de Z)."

#: ../../modules/digital/digital_gates.rst:23
msgid ""
":class:`T(qubit: int)<qilisdk.digital.gates.T>` T gate (π/4 rotation "
"about Z)."
msgstr ""
":class:`T(qubit: int)<qilisdk.digital.gates.T>` Puerta T (rotación π/4 "
"alrededor de Z)."

#: ../../modules/digital/digital_gates.rst:25
msgid ""
":class:`RX(qubit: int, theta: float | Parameter | "
"Term)<qilisdk.digital.gates.RX>` Rotation by angle `theta` around X."
msgstr ""
":class:`RX(qubit: int, theta: float | Parameter | "
"Term)<qilisdk.digital.gates.RX>` Rotación por el ángulo `theta` alrededor de X."

#: ../../modules/digital/digital_gates.rst:27
msgid ""
":class:`RY(qubit: int, theta: float | Parameter | "
"Term)<qilisdk.digital.gates.RY>` Rotation by angle `theta` around Y."
msgstr ""
":class:`RY(qubit: int, theta: float | Parameter | "
"Term)<qilisdk.digital.gates.RY>` Rotación por el ángulo `theta` alrededor de Y."

#: ../../modules/digital/digital_gates.rst:29
msgid ""
":class:`RZ(qubit: int, phi: float | Parameter | "
"Term)<qilisdk.digital.gates.RZ>` Rotation by angle `phi` around Z."
msgstr ""
":class:`RZ(qubit: int, phi: float | Parameter | "
"Term)<qilisdk.digital.gates.RZ>` Rotación por el ángulo `phi` alrededor de Z."

#: ../../modules/digital/digital_gates.rst:31
msgid ""
":class:`U1(qubit: int, *, phi: float | Parameter | "
"Term)<qilisdk.digital.gates.U1>` Phase shift equivalent to RZ plus global"
" phase."
msgstr ""
":class:`U1(qubit: int, *, phi: float | Parameter | "
"Term)<qilisdk.digital.gates.U1>` Desplazamiento de fase equivalente a RZ "
"más fase global."

#: ../../modules/digital/digital_gates.rst:33
msgid ""
":class:`U2(qubit: int, *, phi: float | Parameter | Term, gamma: float | "
"Parameter | Term)<qilisdk.digital.gates.U2>` π/2 Y-rotation sandwiched by"
" Z-rotations."
msgstr ""
":class:`U2(qubit: int, *, phi: float | Parameter | Term, gamma: float | "
"Parameter | Term)<qilisdk.digital.gates.U2>` Rotación Y de π/2 entre "
"rotaciones Z."

#: ../../modules/digital/digital_gates.rst:35
msgid ""
":class:`U3(qubit: int, *, theta: float | Parameter | Term, phi: float | "
"Parameter | Term, gamma: float | Parameter | "
"Term)<qilisdk.digital.gates.U3>` General single-qubit unitary: RZ-RY-RZ "
"decomposition."
msgstr ""
":class:`U3(qubit: int, *, theta: float | Parameter | Term, phi: float | "
"Parameter | Term, gamma: float | Parameter | "
"Term)<qilisdk.digital.gates.U3>` Unitaria general de un qubit: "
"descomposición RZ-RY-RZ."

#: ../../modules/digital/digital_gates.rst:37
msgid ""
":class:`SWAP(a: int, b: int)<qilisdk.digital.gates.SWAP>` Exchanges the "
"states of qubits ``a`` and ``b``."
msgstr ""
":class:`SWAP(a: int, b: int)<qilisdk.digital.gates.SWAP>` Intercambia los "
"estados de los qubits ``a`` y ``b``."

#: ../../modules/digital/digital_gates.rst:39
msgid ""
":class:`CNOT(control: int, target: int)<qilisdk.digital.gates.CNOT>` "
"Controlled-X: flips target if control is 1."
msgstr ""
":class:`CNOT(control: int, target: int)<qilisdk.digital.gates.CNOT>` "
"X controlada: invierte el objetivo si el control es 1."

#: ../../modules/digital/digital_gates.rst:41
msgid ""
":class:`CZ(control: int, target: int)<qilisdk.digital.gates.CZ>` "
"Controlled-Z: applies Z on target if control is 1."
msgstr ""
":class:`CZ(control: int, target: int)<qilisdk.digital.gates.CZ>` "
"Z controlada: aplica Z sobre el objetivo si el control es 1."

#: ../../modules/digital/digital_gates.rst:43
msgid ""
":class:`M(*qubits: int)<qilisdk.digital.gates.M>` Measures the listed "
"qubits in the computational basis."
msgstr ""
":class:`M(*qubits: int)<qilisdk.digital.gates.M>` Mide los qubits "
"listados en la base computacional."

#: ../../modules/digital/digital_gates.rst:47
msgid "Controlled Gates"
msgstr "Puertas controladas"

#: ../../modules/digital/digital_gates.rst:49
msgid ""
"Any basic gate can be turned into a controlled gate using the "
":class:`~qilisdk.digital.gates.Controlled` class:"
msgstr ""
"Cualquier puerta básica puede convertirse en una puerta controlada usando "
"la clase :class:`~qilisdk.digital.gates.Controlled`:"

#: ../../modules/digital/digital_gates.rst:58
msgid ""
"Or alternatively, you can use the "
":meth:`.controlled()<qilisdk.digital.gates.BasicGate.controlled>` method "
"on any gate instance:"
msgstr ""
"O alternativamente, se puede usar el método "
":meth:`.controlled()<qilisdk.digital.gates.BasicGate.controlled>` sobre "
"cualquier instancia de puerta:"

#: ../../modules/digital/digital_gates.rst:69
msgid "Adjoint Gates"
msgstr "Puertas adjuntas"

#: ../../modules/digital/digital_gates.rst:71
msgid ""
"You can create the Hermitian conjugate (dagger) of a gate either using "
"the :class:`~qilisdk.digital.gates.Adjoint` class or using the "
":meth:`.adjoint()<qilisdk.digital.gates.BasicGate.adjoint>` method on any"
" gate instance:"
msgstr ""
"Se puede crear el conjugado hermítico (dagger) de una puerta usando la "
"clase :class:`~qilisdk.digital.gates.Adjoint` o usando el método "
":meth:`.adjoint()<qilisdk.digital.gates.BasicGate.adjoint>` sobre "
"cualquier instancia de puerta:"

#: ../../modules/digital/digital_gates.rst:82
msgid "Exponential Gates"
msgstr "Puertas exponenciales"

#: ../../modules/digital/digital_gates.rst:84
msgid ""
"To apply a gate as an exponential operator, use either the "
":class:`~qilisdk.digital.gates.Exponential` class or the "
":meth:`.exponential()<qilisdk.digital.gates.BasicGate.exponential>` "
"method on any gate instance:"
msgstr ""
"Para aplicar una puerta como operador exponencial, use la clase "
":class:`~qilisdk.digital.gates.Exponential` o el método "
":meth:`.exponential()<qilisdk.digital.gates.BasicGate.exponential>` sobre "
"cualquier instancia de puerta:"

